{"video_id": "TLxtrwKrtV0", "title": "Gaura Purnima 2026 | 1st Anniversary of Arunodaya Kirtan | Sri Madhu Pandit Dasa", "speaker": "HG Madhu Pandit Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TLxtrwKrtV0", "duration": 428, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 4.58, "text": " Hare Krishna, happy Gopurnima to all of you."}, {"start": 5.9, "end": 8.4, "text": " Today we are very happy to share a wonderful milestone"}, {"start": 8.4, "end": 14.46, "text": " by the mercy of Shri Shri Radha Krishna Chandra, Krishna Balaram,"}, {"start": 14.58, "end": 17.16, "text": " Thayagauranga, Srinivasa Govinda, Pralana Shingadev"}, {"start": 17.16, "end": 20.080000000000002, "text": " and the blessings of Vishwaguru Shilaprabhu Paan."}, {"start": 20.12, "end": 28.32, "text": " We have achieved the milestone of completing one full year of Arunodaya Kirtan in Bangalore city."}, {"start": 28.32, "end": 33.16, "text": " One year ago, this initiative began as a humble offering,"}, {"start": 34.58, "end": 38.66, "text": " a sincere desire to bring devotees together from the early hours of the morning"}, {"start": 38.66, "end": 44.400000000000006, "text": " in congregational chanting of the holy names of the Lord in the streets of Bangalore."}, {"start": 45.04, "end": 50.120000000000005, "text": " Today, by Lord Chaitanya's grace, it has become a vibrant spiritual activity"}, {"start": 50.120000000000005, "end": 52.480000000000004, "text": " touching thousands of lives."}, {"start": 53.5, "end": 55.92, "text": " When we perform congregational chanting,"}, {"start": 56.519999999999996, "end": 57.94, "text": " we are directly,"}, {"start": 58.32, "end": 61.32, "text": " directly connected to the mission of Shri Chaitanya Mahaprabhu."}, {"start": 62.32, "end": 67.32, "text": " Shilaprabhupada explains that Lord Chaitanya, the greatest proponent of love of God"}, {"start": 68.32, "end": 71.32, "text": " and the father of congregational chanting of the holy name,"}, {"start": 72.32, "end": 76.32, "text": " personally inaugurated the religion of this age, Nama Sankirtana."}, {"start": 77.32, "end": 78.32, "text": " Mahaprabhu declared,"}, {"start": 79.32, "end": 84.32, "text": " I shall personally inaugurate the religion of this age, Nama Sankirtana,"}, {"start": 84.32, "end": 86.32, "text": " the congregation chanting of the holy names."}, {"start": 88.32000000000001, "end": 91.32000000000001, "text": " He said, I will make the world dance in ecstasy."}, {"start": 92.32000000000001, "end": 94.32000000000001, "text": " And what is this process?"}, {"start": 94.32000000000001, "end": 96.32000000000001, "text": " Shilaprabhupada beautifully explains"}, {"start": 96.32000000000001, "end": 99.32000000000001, "text": " that there is no pre-qualification required,"}, {"start": 99.32000000000001, "end": 101.32000000000001, "text": " no material condition to be fulfilled."}, {"start": 102.32000000000001, "end": 106.32000000000001, "text": " Because our dormant love of God already exists within our heart"}, {"start": 106.32000000000001, "end": 112.32000000000001, "text": " and it can be awakened simply by chanting Hare Krishna Mahamantra daily"}, {"start": 112.32000000000001, "end": 114.32000000000001, "text": " with sincerity and enthusiasm."}, {"start": 114.32000000000001, "end": 117.32000000000001, "text": " Through this joyful process of chanting and dancing,"}, {"start": 117.32000000000001, "end": 122.32000000000001, "text": " one gradually develops genuine love for the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 123.32000000000001, "end": 127.32000000000001, "text": " This is the great mercy of Lord in this age."}, {"start": 128.32, "end": 130.32, "text": " There is no requirement for high birth,"}, {"start": 130.32, "end": 132.32, "text": " no requirement for scholarship"}, {"start": 132.32, "end": 134.32, "text": " and no complicated ritual."}, {"start": 134.32, "end": 136.32, "text": " Simply chant,"}, {"start": 136.32, "end": 140.32, "text": " Hare Krishna, Hare Krishna, Krishna Krishna, Hare Hare,"}, {"start": 140.32, "end": 143.32, "text": " Hare Rama, Hare Rama, Rama Rama, Hare Hare."}, {"start": 143.32, "end": 146.32, "text": " And over the past year, we have witnessed the results practically."}, {"start": 147.32, "end": 150.32, "text": " Arunodaya Kirtan has been conducted in so many places,"}, {"start": 150.32, "end": 152.32, "text": " in temples, in homes,"}, {"start": 152.32, "end": 155.32, "text": " during festivals, in the community gatherings."}, {"start": 155.32, "end": 161.32, "text": " During Janmashtami, Ram Navami, Nithyananda Trodeshi,"}, {"start": 161.32, "end": 166.32, "text": " Narsimha Jayanti, Ratha Yatra and many more occasions,"}, {"start": 166.32, "end": 172.32, "text": " thousands have participated in Bangalore city in chanting and dancing."}, {"start": 173.32, "end": 176.32, "text": " Along with the Kirtan, Prasadam has been distributed abundantly."}, {"start": 177.32, "end": 180.32, "text": " Following the instructions of Srimad Bhagavatam."}, {"start": 185.32, "end": 188.32, "text": " In this age, intelligent persons worship"}, {"start": 188.32, "end": 192.32, "text": " the Supreme Lord by the sacrifice of Sankirtana."}, {"start": 192.32, "end": 194.32, "text": " Srila Prabhupada describes"}, {"start": 194.32, "end": 198.32, "text": " how even the wild animals in the forest of Jarikanda"}, {"start": 198.32, "end": 201.32, "text": " joined Chaitanya Mahaprabhu's Sankirtana."}, {"start": 202.32, "end": 204.32, "text": " Today the world is disturbed"}, {"start": 204.32, "end": 206.32, "text": " socially, politically, economically"}, {"start": 206.32, "end": 209.32, "text": " and in so many other ways."}, {"start": 209.32, "end": 213.32, "text": " There is visible strife between individuals,"}, {"start": 213.32, "end": 215.32, "text": " divisions between communities,"}, {"start": 215.32, "end": 217.32, "text": " tensions among nations."}, {"start": 217.32, "end": 221.32, "text": " So much mistrust, conflict and anxiety."}, {"start": 221.32, "end": 225.32, "text": " They have become common feature of modern life."}, {"start": 225.32, "end": 227.32, "text": " In such a disturbed climate,"}, {"start": 227.32, "end": 230.32, "text": " congregational chanting of the holy names"}, {"start": 230.32, "end": 234.32, "text": " offer a unifying spiritual platform."}, {"start": 234.32, "end": 236.32, "text": " By bringing people together,"}, {"start": 236.32, "end": 238.32, "text": " beyond the differences of background,"}, {"start": 238.32, "end": 240.32, "text": " status and ideology,"}, {"start": 240.32, "end": 242.32, "text": " we are helping them reconnect"}, {"start": 242.32, "end": 246.32, "text": " with the common foundation of love of God."}, {"start": 246.32, "end": 247.32, "text": " Through Nama Sankirtana,"}, {"start": 247.32, "end": 249.32, "text": " our hearts are purified,"}, {"start": 249.32, "end": 252.32, "text": " relationships are harmonized"}, {"start": 252.32, "end": 255.32, "text": " and genuine unity is achieved among all."}, {"start": 255.32, "end": 258.32, "text": " The more we perform this Sankirtana Yajna,"}, {"start": 258.32, "end": 261.32, "text": " the more we advance in love of God."}, {"start": 261.32, "end": 264.32, "text": " Therefore, on this important occasion"}, {"start": 264.32, "end": 265.32, "text": " of completing"}, {"start": 265.32, "end": 267.32, "text": " one year of Arunodaya Kirtan,"}, {"start": 267.32, "end": 270.32, "text": " I would like to encourage all of you,"}, {"start": 270.32, "end": 273.32, "text": " let us continue with our mission"}, {"start": 273.32, "end": 275.32, "text": " with even more enthusiasm."}, {"start": 275.32, "end": 279.32, "text": " Let every home become a center for Kirtan."}, {"start": 279.32, "end": 281.32, "text": " If you have the facility,"}, {"start": 281.32, "end": 283.32, "text": " invite devotees to your home,"}, {"start": 283.32, "end": 284.32, "text": " distribute prasadam,"}, {"start": 284.32, "end": 286.32, "text": " hold Kirtan for a few hours,"}, {"start": 286.32, "end": 288.32, "text": " at least once a week."}, {"start": 288.32, "end": 290.32, "text": " Gather your friends,"}, {"start": 290.32, "end": 292.32, "text": " your family, your neighbors."}, {"start": 292.32, "end": 294.32, "text": " Just as the rising sun dissipates"}, {"start": 294.32, "end": 296.32, "text": " darkness,"}, {"start": 296.32, "end": 298.32, "text": " congregational chanting dissipates"}, {"start": 298.32, "end": 301.32, "text": " the darkness of ignorance from the heart."}, {"start": 304.32, "end": 306.32, "text": " Lord Chaitanya predicted"}, {"start": 306.32, "end": 308.32, "text": " that this Sankirtana movement would spread"}, {"start": 308.32, "end": 311.32, "text": " every town and village of the world."}, {"start": 311.32, "end": 313.32, "text": " Srila Prabhupada established ISKCON"}, {"start": 313.32, "end": 315.32, "text": " with the purpose of teaching"}, {"start": 315.32, "end": 318.32, "text": " this very same process."}, {"start": 318.32, "end": 321.32, "text": " Let us follow in the footsteps of our Gurudev,"}, {"start": 321.32, "end": 323.32, "text": " Srila Prabhupada."}, {"start": 323.32, "end": 325.32, "text": " I would also like to invite"}, {"start": 325.32, "end": 327.32, "text": " all devotees to participate"}, {"start": 327.32, "end": 329.32, "text": " for the Arunodaya Kirtan"}, {"start": 329.32, "end": 331.32, "text": " on 3rd March,"}, {"start": 331.32, "end": 333.32, "text": " Gaurapurnima,"}, {"start": 333.32, "end": 335.32, "text": " the most auspicious day"}, {"start": 335.32, "end": 337.32, "text": " of Lord Chaitanya's appearance,"}, {"start": 337.32, "end": 339.32, "text": " who is the inaugurator"}, {"start": 339.32, "end": 341.32, "text": " of the Sankirtana movement"}, {"start": 341.32, "end": 343.32, "text": " 500 years back."}, {"start": 343.32, "end": 345.32, "text": " This year, it falls on a weekday."}, {"start": 345.32, "end": 347.32, "text": " You may have office commitments,"}, {"start": 347.32, "end": 349.32, "text": " important meetings,"}, {"start": 349.32, "end": 351.32, "text": " or responsibility for preparing"}, {"start": 351.32, "end": 353.32, "text": " your children for school. Yet,"}, {"start": 353.32, "end": 355.32, "text": " in your schedule,"}, {"start": 355.32, "end": 357.32, "text": " rise a little earlier if needed."}, {"start": 357.32, "end": 359.32, "text": " Plan your day in advance"}, {"start": 359.32, "end": 361.32, "text": " and make it a firm commitment"}, {"start": 361.32, "end": 364.32, "text": " not to miss this Arunodaya Kirtan"}, {"start": 364.32, "end": 366.32, "text": " of 3rd March,"}, {"start": 366.32, "end": 368.32, "text": " 2026."}, {"start": 368.32, "end": 370.32, "text": " Let us assemble in large numbers,"}, {"start": 370.32, "end": 372.32, "text": " in thousands,"}, {"start": 372.32, "end": 374.32, "text": " and offer our collective chanting"}, {"start": 374.32, "end": 376.32, "text": " as our heartful tribute"}, {"start": 376.32, "end": 379.32, "text": " to Lord Sri Chaitanya Mahaprabhu."}, {"start": 379.32, "end": 381.32, "text": " On this sacred morning,"}, {"start": 381.32, "end": 382.32, "text": " let us begin the day"}, {"start": 382.32, "end": 384.32, "text": " with the holy names"}, {"start": 384.32, "end": 386.32, "text": " and receive His special mercy."}, {"start": 386.32, "end": 388.32, "text": " Let us take this Arunodaya Kirtan"}, {"start": 388.32, "end": 390.32, "text": " to more areas, more communities,"}, {"start": 390.32, "end": 392.32, "text": " more homes."}, {"start": 392.32, "end": 394.32, "text": " Let thousands become lakhs."}, {"start": 394.32, "end": 396.32, "text": " Let lakhs become millions."}, {"start": 396.32, "end": 398.32, "text": " Simply chant with faith and enthusiasm."}, {"start": 398.32, "end": 400.32, "text": " Distribute prasadam with joy."}, {"start": 400.32, "end": 402.32, "text": " There is no loss."}, {"start": 402.32, "end": 404.32, "text": " There is only gain, spiritual happiness,"}, {"start": 404.32, "end": 406.32, "text": " purification, unity,"}, {"start": 406.32, "end": 408.32, "text": " and ultimately,"}, {"start": 408.32, "end": 410.32, "text": " love of God."}, {"start": 410.32, "end": 412.32, "text": " This is Krishna Sankirtanam."}, {"start": 412.32, "end": 414.32, "text": " Sisi Go Nithaya Ki Jai."}, {"start": 414.32, "end": 417.32, "text": " Arunodaya Sankirtan Ki Jai."}, {"start": 417.32, "end": 420.32, "text": " Vishwaguru Sheela Prabhupada Ki Jai."}]}